These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, december, may, march
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, grapes, pineapple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, western, sports, martial-arts
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, japanese, thai, indonesian
 1. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the japanese##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating pineapple##1
 3. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the thai is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the mexican is on the far left##1
10. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| Birthday    | may   | december       | february | march   |
| Food        | banana    | pineapple  | grapes      | apple |
| Movie-Genre         | martial-arts      | western | sports         | time-travel   |
| Nationality   | mexican | japanese       | thai        | indonesian   |

