.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, coffee, almond-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, d&b, pop, classical
House: farmhouse, craftsman, cape-cod, modern
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, roller, tram, trike
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the fan of r&b##1
3. the person driving the tram is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking fanta is between the fan of d&b and the person driving the car##2
5. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
6. the modern house is the person driving the trike##1
7. the farmhouse house is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
9. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Beverage           | sprite | fanta | almond-milk | coffee |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | pop | d&b         | classical      |
| House         | cape-cod      | craftsman    | modern         | farmhouse   |
| Transport     | car         | roller    | trike          | tram         |

