.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, architect, dressmaker, doctor
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, gospel, indie, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, subway, trike, scooter
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite, milk, soy-milk
 1. the fan of indie is the dressmaker##1
 2. the fan of folk is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the doctor is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of rock##1
 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 8. the person driving the van is between the person drinking milk and the fan of gospel##2
 9. the doctor is on the left of the project-manager##1
10. the architect is on the left or right of the doctor##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Job          | architect | doctor  | project-manager | dressmaker      |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | rock    | gospel      | indie      |
| Transport           | scooter     | van     | subway         | trike   |
| Beverage         | milk | almond-milk | sprite     | soy-milk |

