.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, lavender, turquise, grey
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, milk, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, canadian, french, polish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, siglo, alhambra, tiparillo
