2. the australian is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person who likes turquise is the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
5. the french is the person drinking cola##1
6. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
7. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
8. the person who likes grey is between the montecristo-smoker and the polish##2
9. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Color           | purple     | grey | lavender | turquise |
| Beverage   | milk     | almond-milk       | water      | cola   |
| Nationality   | canadian   | australian   | polish    | french       |
| Cigar           | montecristo | siglo        | alhambra    | tiparillo        |

