.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, social-worker, scientist, doctor
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, helicopter, van, tram
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, turtle, cat, ferret
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, basketball, cycling, ice-hockey
 1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
 2. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 3. the police-officer is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 5. the doctor is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 8. the scientist is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the owner of the ferret is between the police-officer and the owner of the cat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Job      | doctor | police-officer | scientist     | social-worker       |
| Transport          | trike   | tram    | van | helicopter       |
| Pet   | chinchilla     | turtle       | ferret    | cat     |
| Sport         | cycling  | ice-hockey  | badminton | basketball |

