 7. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
 8. the person traveling to boston is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
10. the police-officer is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to prague is the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |      3      |     4      |
