 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person playing poker and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 6. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person traveling to venice##2
 8. the person driving the boat is the person playing whist##1
 9. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |      4       |
| Game         | poker | bridge     | domino  | whist |
| Transport   | tram      | bus  | motorbike   | boat          |
| City           | colone      | venice       | berlin    | hamburg         |
| Sport         | tennis     | basketball | baseball | parkour      |

