The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, soul, blues, rock
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, dog, fish, pony
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, disaster, satire, epic
 1. the owner of the pony is the person watching epic movies##1
 2. the fan of reggae is between the owner of the dog and the owner of the pony##2
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the owner of the fish is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is the owner of the pony##1
 6. the person playing snooker is between the person watching satire movies and the person playing canasta##2
 7. the person playing snooker is the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the owner of the fish is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 9. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person playing chess##1
11. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |       4       |
| Game   | canasta    | snooker  | monopoly       | chess  |
| Music-Genre     | soul    | reggae | blues | rock        |
| Pet     | pony       | fish     | dog          | chinchilla    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | zombie    | satire     | disaster |

