.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, card-games, dancing, gardening
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, orange, red, aquamarine
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, 7up, cola
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 4. the person who likes orange is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person who likes orange and the person drinking mirinda##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who likes orange##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby          | card-games | gardening   | dancing   | rock-climbing |
| Color           | azure   | red     | orange   | aquamarine |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Beverage         | mirinda    | iced-tea | cola | 7up    |

 